Package scalf.cmsc335.finalProject Description

Contains all of the classes for the TrafficSimulation program (CMSC335 Final Project).

The classes in within this package and sub-packages all support the functionality of the project. The classes and interfaces in this package were used in the creation of a multi-threaded GUI application.

The interfaces in this package are used to reduce dependency between classes. It's not an ideal implementation, but I wanted to get used to the idea of abstracting classes.

The main class for the program is TrafficSimulation.
